{"tid":696713,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"海水魚開缸","createTime":"2018-06-10T10:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T11:22:38.000Z","uid":146214,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8daaadf299fa031c7b5b2017b355f28905e8687f","tid":696713,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:56:20.000Z","msg":"之前都開過post問，但因為咁多位師兄都話好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以放棄<br />\n但最近搵咗好多資料，討論區既師兄都話純養魚甚至只需要一個濾器就ok(當然要勤換水啦）小弟只係諗住養魚同少量珊瑚，應該只要化氮、過濾器、氣泵就ok，養魚就貴有貴玩，平有平玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知各位巴打點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n預氣材1000內，學生哥，假期做下part time添設下"},{"pid":"1d2a8a169bcd120c0b175c50ae29f0a1d6e85cda","tid":696713,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:57:45.000Z","msg":"養下小丑仔藍吊果d唔洗好貴啦"},{"pid":"2d9ab53cd2ed58890668ce487fa0c3cb2dadb9fc","tid":696713,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d2a8a169bcd120c0b175c50ae29f0a1d6e85cda","tid":696713,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:57:45.000Z","msg":"養下小丑仔藍吊果d唔洗好貴啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:00:39.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢兩隻都係想養嘅魚之一，又平又粗養"},{"pid":"cbf3ca44be2bd53c3a589e9fbc2cd5f061ae8bdb","tid":696713,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"最平可以點養？D水就咁加鹽？"},{"pid":"09528fdcd8bf65558649b76cf2c38908cd2703f8","tid":696713,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:05:12.000Z","msg":"小丑魚全部都係野口<br />\n唔可以人工繁殖<br />\n買少見少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f375e26d993a4248e50f3ddb51eddb98177dc0d3","tid":696713,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbf3ca44be2bd53c3a589e9fb